<h2 id="phonenumber">PhoneNumber</h2>

<p>A phone number, represented in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E.123" class="external">E.123</a> international notation (eg â€œ+6421537663â€). We usually use this for receiving text messages.</p>

